<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I was under the impression that dual wielding the best 1h weapons always outdamages the best 2h weapons, and rogues should outdamage monks when attacking from behind because of backstab.<P><BR>The main concern of wizards is not short term DPS, it's <B>average</B> DPS which is about 33 DPS with med, clarity 2, and best bard song casting solist's ice spear without resists, assuming the accepted value of 25 mana per tick meditation is accurate. I have no clue of an average DPS figure that accounts for resists, though.<P>Arlina
</FONT>
