For those who STILL don't get it...<P>Wizards are built to kill multiple mobs AT THE SAME TIME.  We are optimized for that and suck at everything else.  Now, you have a choice...<P>1)  Continue to whine about being crappy for single target continous killing, or<P>2)  Start doing some AoE and have more fun and get more XP than you ever have in EQ.<P>It's up to you.  However, arguing about how much damage soandso does per second is completely irrelevant.  Did Verant EVER say that we were supposed to be good at killing single targets?  NO.  <P>There is a price to pay for all your abilities.<P>--------------------<P>Bethude<BR>59 Evoker
